title: Silent Warrior [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
The protagonist is a special forces fighter. During the operation "Storm," your task was to eliminate the leader of a large drug cartel. You flew on a helicopter to carry out the mission. Everything seemed to go according to plan, but then suddenly your helicopter is shot down. When you wake up, you realize that you are trapped and you shouldn't bother waiting for help, you're on your own...
